Text.Value: Do you know anything about the dictionary I found?
Lady who brought me here carried it... Hid it from monster...
What did the monster look like?
Leave.
Tried but... couldn't drink... retching and gagging... then monster arrived...
Did the lady kill you?
Tall... long hair... terrible eyes...
What happened when you got here?
Dalyria...
How did you end up here?
Lady carried it... Hid it from monster...
She brought me here... promised food... shelter...
Victoria... orphan...
*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*
*The corpse regards you lifelessly.*
Who are you?
Lady promised me food... shelter... took me here...
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*
Furious... she tried to disobey... not drink thinking creatures... he dragged her away...
She held me... bit me... blood everywhere...
What lady? Do you know her name?
*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*

Synopsis: SwD dialog with a dead girl that can be found in one of the bedrooms in Cazador's Palace
